{
  "stem": "22047.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I've got a couple of funny stories that I'd like to tell about what happened during this, and I'll tell a traumatic story.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe I'll tell that first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was told to take a patrol out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were going to-- to go to a-- a city named Metz and join with another patrol and capture the town and hold it for a pending attack.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that would be a hub of the attack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were supposed to get there and hold the town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, we didn't get very far.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We got across the valley and went up the other side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And one of my guys stepped on a shoe mine and blew his foot off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so I called back to say that, you know, we've run into a minefield and I don't think we can proceed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the other unit was having trouble too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They ran into a terrible fight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so we were both told to come back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had minefields down in front of our positions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I knew the pathway through the minefield.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I said, I want permission to come back through the minefield, because going-- coming back the same way we went out is pretty dangerous, because if somebody sees us coming out, they're going to wait and watch us come back.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I said, I want to come back through the minefield.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my request was denied.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went back the same route we came out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And sure enough, we're halfway across this valley, and a-- and a mortar round lights right in the middle of us, killed the guy that had his foot blown off, plus one of the stretcher-bearers.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got shrapnel hit me in the neck, but didn't actually wound me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It knocked me down.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
